subtitleNullable: dataset for dog breed classification using cnn
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset contains faces of famous people and various dogbreeds. The faces are contained in lfw folder and dog faces in dogImages folder. Primary purpose of this dataset is dog breed classification.


### Acknowledgements
I came across this dataset through udacity's nanodegree program. Thanks to udacity's program and project that enabled me to ask and answer many questions with this dataset.


### Inspiration

I am also attaching my kernel which answers question like the breed  the dog image belongs too using a CNN from scratch and transfer learning. Alternative questions that could be asked are how the face detector can be made resilient to adversarial attacks etc.
